This applicaton can send any HCI command via UART and it can also download the bt patchram, its parameter is same as brcm_patchram_plus

To build this tool in Android:

Copy to any folder in your android code


To build this FM radio in Ubuntu/Linux, just "make" it.

Before run this demo, please run the hciattach utility firstly.





1. To start application

./app_vsc -d --patchram PATCHRAM_NAME.hcd --baudrate 1500000 --no2bytes --tosleep 5000 /dev/TTYDEVICE


2. send command parameter

Egï¼š

hcicmd 03 0c 00
